HEADWORD: macadamia nut
<hw>macadamia nut</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The hard-shelled nut of the
<spn>Macadamia ternifolia</spn>, or the delicious edible nut without its
shell; large quantities are produced in Hawaii and sold
commercially.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

